  "subject": "Update dmi-properties when updating additional-properties to stay in sync",
  "commit_message": "Update dmi-properties when updating additional-properties to stay in sync\n\n- Added updateDmiPropertiesIfExists to keep dmi-properties in sync\n  when additionalProperties are updated via the inventory API\n- Added getMergedAdditionalProperties to merge existing and updated\n  properties before serializing to the dmi-properties leaf\n- Only updates dmi-properties when it already exists (model-agnostic)\n- Added manual demo document for K8s + Postman verification\n\nIssue-ID: CPS-3219\n\nChange-Id: Ice188b97b597517574b25d1c426a93fd70ac8b10\nSigned-off-by: egernug <gerard.nugent@est.tech>\n",
